description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we’re looking for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Degree educated, enthusiastic and motivated individual&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Passion for Healthcare, wanting to make a differences to the local community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll get&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;fully-qualified accountant with the CIMA or ACCA qualification with all the training costs paid for and the opportunity to gain financial experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flexible working and support through your training period and being part of a fantastic team to launch your finance and healthcare career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll have an opportunity to progress while also earning a competitive salary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;St George’s University Hospital is a thriving Foundation Trust at the heart of an integrated healthcare system. One that delivers improved patient care at a community, hospital and specialist setting, supported by a unique and nationally recognised programme of research, education and employee engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our finance experts play a critical role in the success of our organisation and by joining our Management Accountant team, you&#39;ll have the chance to make a real impact early on. The team works with the Operational and Clinical staff to create the best patient care possible and supports the Trusts in delivering its strategic objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We also expect all our staff to share the values that are important to the Trust, being Excellent, Kind, Responsible &amp; Respectful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameLucy JamesJob titleHead of FinanceEmail addressLucy.James@stgeorges.nhs.ukAdditional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Any questions, please contact Michael Armour (Michael.Armour@stgeorges.nhs.uk) or Lucy James Lucy.James@stgeorges.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
